  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13101732/adobestock_639185861-1.jpg" alt="getting to resort" data-udi="umb://media/3a28d9d46c8a4e9d9625e28b34ba50da" /></p>
<h3>Freedom and flexibility to choose how you enjoy your journey with Inghams.</h3>
<p>Getting to your dream destination is easy on an Inghams Walking holiday. With the choice of plane, train or driving yourself, you can spend the journey to your chosen resort how you like. Whether that's soaking up the sights on a train through the mountains, enjoying the freedom time on your self-drive journey or enjoying views from above from your plane seat.</p>
<p><strong>Fly</strong></p>
<p>With departures from airports located throughout the UK, finding a flight that fits your holiday plans is a breeze. We’re all about options, ensuring your journey is smooth from takeoff to touchdown.</p>
<p><strong>Rail</strong></p>
<p>We offer train packages from the UK into many of our walking resorts, making it as easy as possible for you to choose a lower impact, greener holiday. Sit back, relax and experience the magic of the journey whilst soaking up some stunning landscapes as you go.</p>
<p><strong>Coach</strong><br />Our transfers are usually by coach, so you can simply kick back, unwind and enjoy the views along the way. Leave the driving to us.</p>
<p><strong>Self-Drive</strong></p>
<p>Fly in, pick up your car, and start exploring. We’ve mapped out some great itineraries to ensure every twist and turn is a visual treat, and every pit stop, a memorable moment.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/02a5945a51fe4587bf5aa72b66298bea" href="/{localLink:umb://document/02a5945a51fe4587bf5aa72b66298bea}?&amp;from=QQS" title="Switzerland" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn--mid c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="?&amp;from=QQS">View Switzerland Holiday Deals</a></p>
<p> </p>]]></bodyText>
